  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111730/extras/bca57c920157599f78ac0478f112e832.avif?t=1728358598\" width=230 height=86 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The city has been taken over by zombies! </h2>Traverse the procedurally generated streets filled with the undead to find the resources you need to survive! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111730/extras/f95d97ccbd6d080b8510c5c51f9098f2.avif?t=1728358598\" width=64 height=64 /></span><br><strong>Shoot your way through the zombies</strong> but make sure you preserve your ammo. You can only carry so many rounds at a time and you may wish you didn't waste your last round on a single zombie you could've easily avoided. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111730/extras/bdcbe8c7b6598bd206417986fb28783a.avif?t=1728358598\" width=64 height=64 /></span><br><strong>Fight your way through with your handy knife</strong> but be warned; knife fighting zombies usually means you're going to get bit and infected. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111730/extras/1c3bbd49acc7dc4990b441872a551c3f.avif?t=1728358598\" width=64 height=64 /></span><br><strong>Stave off the infection</strong> by snagging a Z Juice before your immune system gives up on you and you perish from a bite.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111730/extras/53c2202f9dd6d827ab8196616fd07faa.avif?t=1728358598\" width=64 height=64 /></span> <br><strong>Collect Z Coins</strong> to upgrade your core attributes, ammo carrying capacity, and knife fighting ability. Find these coins by getting to hard-to-reach areas and fighting off as many zombies as possible.",
